name: Dismissal of indictment
text: Any indictment which is based upon a grand jury proceeding in which a violation of section 612-56, 612-57, or 612-58 has occurred may be subject to dismissal without prejudice by an appropriate state court in the exercise of its discretion.  Motion for such dismissal may be made by either party or the court. [L 1980, c 209, §10]
